downloadTitle: Dynamics 365 for Project Service Automation Power BI Change Tracking Solution
downloadDescription: Dynamics 365 for PSA solution that enables Data Export Service change tracking for Power BI solution template

downloadFile.name: PSA Power BI solution template change tracking solution.EXE
downloadFile.url: https://download.microsoft.com/download/0/c/4/0c471846-519e-42ba-b85e-99d55d3e7963/PSA Power BI solution template change tracking solution.EXE

detailsSection: This self-extracting archive contains a managed solution that enables change tracking for Dynamics 365 Project Service Automation entities necessary for the Data Export Service.  The Data Export Service extracts the relevant entities to the SQL Azure dB used by the Power BI solution template.  More information on the solution template is available on the Power BI solution template site.
detailsSection_file_name: PSA Power BI solution template change tracking solution.EXE
systemRequirementsSection:
Windows 10
A working Dynamics 365 for Project Service Automation implementation
installInstructionSection:
Download the self-extracting archive file and open it.

Import the managed solution zip file into your Dynamics 365 for Project Service Automation instance.

You can follow these instructions for importing solutions on TechNet: Import, update and export solutions
